page.title: 07MY DAY
page.content: In the morning I get up and have a wash at 7.55am. I then go downstairs and make my breakfast. I eat my breakfast and then clean my teeth at 8.15. At 8.30am I get ready for school I arrive at school at 8.45am. I then play until I ring the bell at 9am. I begin my lessons at9.30am. after assembly.I have a 15 minute lunch break at 10.40am. At noon when lessons are over I go for my dinner. The afternoon lessons start at 1.15pm. I have another break at 2.30pm. School finishes at 3.45pm. When I get home I watch television until I have my tea at 5pm.Then I watch television again until 6pm when I wash the dishes. When I have done those I play with my brother until 7pm. I watch television until 9pm. when I have my supper and then I go to bed at about 9.30pm.
